---
title: Mushroom Ragout with Crispy Polenta Cakes and Tangy Arugula Salad
description: Mushrooms, thyme, and garlic are a match made in heaven. Folded into a cream sauce over pillows of crispy polenta, it doesn’t get much better than this. A tangy balsamic-arugula salad is the perfect counterpoint.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/570c0c05fd2cb9e15d8b4567.jpg
